data.description: Sharp. Updated. Impeccably Clean. 2309 Woodbine Rd in Hopewell Twp is move in ready! Go through the front door and you'll see freshly refinished hardwood floors throughout, a wood burning fireplace in the living room, a dining room, two bedrooms, a first floor full bath, an updated kitchen with luxury vinyl, white cabinetry, quartz countertops, a tile backsplash, stainless appliances, and a door that leads out to the HUGE enclosed side porch. Upstairs you'll find a sitting area, a huge walk in closet, and a large master bedroom with a walk in closet. The basement is finished and features luxury vinyl flooring, high ceilings, recessed lights, an updated full bath, 2 flex spaces, laundry, and a garage. Outside the home you'll find a nice back yard, a flat two car wide driveway for extra parking, and a shed. Another key feature of the home is the incredible amount of storage it has. You get all of this in a great location close to Treehaven neighborhood pool and all the area has to offer!
